Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:02.51,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:236630,242510}Apparently there's a mysterious figure reigning over them at the summit. I'm investigating that right now.{NOTE:どうやら謎の人物が頂点に君臨しているようですが現在鋭意調査中っす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:07.18,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:242510,247180}Who are the Ebon Riders and what is their goal?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズとは何者で目的はいったい何なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.89,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:247180,249890}I'm going to find that out in my own way.{NOTE:僕なりに調べてみようと思ってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:13.48,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:249890,253480}Lilia seems to have caught a clue about them as well.{NOTE:リリアが連中について手掛かりをつかんだらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.65,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:253480,255650}Could you go assist her with her research?{NOTE:一緒に調べに向かってくれるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.61,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:255650,257610}Why don't you go, Captain?{NOTE:隊長は行かないんすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.82,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:257610,260820}I have other businesses I must attend to.{NOTE:私は他の調査があってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.91,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:260820,263910}You're extremely capable.{NOTE:お前がいれば百人力だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.03,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:263910,266030}I'm counting on you.{NOTE:頼りにしてるぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.33,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:266030,267330}Oh, thank you!{NOTE:あざっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.24,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:267330,268240}It'll be my pleasure!{NOTE:喜んで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.29,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:269740,273290}{\i1}Scrivener Journal Entry #21567.{NOTE:書士隊日誌ナンバー21567。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.12,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:273290,275120}{\i1}Reporter: Pappan.{NOTE:文責パパン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.92,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:275120,278920}{\i1}Survey day 1. It's sunny with no clouds.{NOTE:調査１日目。雲一つない快晴なり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.30,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:278920,281300}{\i1}I'm in Gildegaran waiting for my traveling companion.{NOTE:ギルデカランにて同行者を待つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.84,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:284130,286840}Captain Simone is away today.{NOTE:今日はシモーヌ隊長がいないからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.47,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:286840,289470}I have to take care of my junior well.{NOTE:僕がしっかり後輩を引っ張らなくっちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.10,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:289470,291100}Vice Captain!{NOTE:副隊長～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.89,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:291100,292890}Sorry I made you wait!{NOTE:お待たせしました！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.31,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:292890,294310}Good morning.{NOTE:おはようございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.69,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:294310,295690}Long time no see.{NOTE:ぶりぶりーっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.27,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:295690,298270}Where are we going to first?{NOTE:でまずはどこへ向かう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.11,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:298270,301110}Would you care for a stylish cafe?{NOTE:おしゃれなカフェで腹ごしらえでもしちゃう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:06.86,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:303400,306860}J-J-Just kidding! Hahaha…{NOTE:ななな、なーんてね。ハハハ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.99,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:306860,308990}Ah, are you hungry?{NOTE:あっおなかすいてるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.83,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:308990,310830}Did you eat your breakfast?{NOTE:朝食べ損なったんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:310830,312950}Should I make an Energy Drink?{NOTE:元気ドリンコを作りましょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:16.08,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:312950,316080}Oh, um, thank you, but that's okay.{NOTE:うんごめん大丈夫だよ。ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.21,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:316080,318210}So where are we headed?{NOTE:でどこへ向かうんだっけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.75,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:318210,319750}We're going to Omi Valley.{NOTE:オミの谷…です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:26.09,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:322210,326090}Speaking of Omi Valley, it's said to be a Hunters' training ground.{NOTE:オミの谷といえばハンターの修練場と呼ばれてるくらい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.26,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:326090,329260}It is a place where you can find ferocious monsters in clusters.{NOTE:凶暴なモンスターがうじゃうじゃといる所だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.56,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:329260,330560}We'll be fine.{NOTE:大丈夫ですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.27,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:330560,332270}Oh, so you have a plan?{NOTE:何か策があるんだね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.68,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:332270,334680}I knew one could rely on you, Lilia!{NOTE:さっすがリリア！頼りになる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.44,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:334680,336440}But I don't have one.{NOTE:いえないですけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.98,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:336440,337980}Then why are we going there?{NOTE:えっじゃあ何で!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.06,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:337980,339060}Just my intuition.{NOTE:直感です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.36,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:339060,340360}Eh…?{NOTE:え～っ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.19,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:341610,344190}{\i1}My companion is enthusiastic about research.{NOTE:同行者は研究熱心ではあるが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.95,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:344190,345950}{\i1}But sometimes she's kind of reckless.{NOTE:…無鉄砲な面あり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.66,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:345950,349660}{\i1}There's also room for doubt in her planning ability.{NOTE:また計画性については疑問の余地がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.95,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:349660,351950}It's going to be a long journey…{NOTE:幸先不安な旅だなぁ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:52.87,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:351950,352870}Ah?{NOTE:あっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.75,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:355200,356750}W-What?{NOTE:な、何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.50,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:357540,360500}{\i1}I've never understood it.{NOTE:私ずっと分からなかったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:04.26,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:360500,364260}{\i1}Why the Ebon Riders have been collecting our Kinship Stones.{NOTE:なぜブラックライダーズが絆石を集めているのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.97,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:364260,366970}{\i1}But after investigating an old document,\NI found out about a village…{NOTE:でもある古文書を調べていて}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:13.68,Default,Lilia,1,1,0,,{TIME:366970,373680}{\i1}…where the secret art of syncing with a monster using\Nthe power of Kinship Stones was passed down through generations.{NOTE:絆石の力を使ってモンスターとシンクロする秘術が代々伝わる村があるらしいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.85,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:373680,375850}{\i1}I'm not sure about the location of that village.{NOTE:どこにあるか分からないんですけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.02,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:375850,378020}{\i1}But there's an important lead.{NOTE:…一つだけ手掛かりが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.23,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:378020,381230}The painter of the picture is called\NMr. Pollock and he's from the Omi Valley.{NOTE:絵を描いた人はオミの谷のポロックさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:25.32,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:381230,385320}Even though it's a pretty old picture,\Nthere might still be people who know him there.{NOTE:古い絵ですけどまだ村に知っている人がいるかも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.28,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:385320,388280}They might have more valuable information as well.{NOTE:その方なら何か知っているんじゃないかと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:35.24,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:389660,395240}So the Ebon Riders are collecting the Kinship Stones\Nin order to obtain that secret art?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズはその秘術を行うために絆石を集めているってこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:395240,396950}I don't have any evidence for that.{NOTE:確証はないんですけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.75,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:398160,399750}Hmm.{NOTE:うーん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:48.55,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:399750,408550}Intuition is important, but our Scriveners' job\Nis to draw conclusions based on scientific evidence.{NOTE:直感も大事だけど僕たち書士隊の仕事は地味にこつこつ確証を積み上げて事実を導き出すことだよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:52.22,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:408550,412220}It's dangerous to depend on your intuition too much.{NOTE:直感に頼り過ぎるのはちょっと危険かな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:53.76,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:412220,413760}I'm sorry.{NOTE:すみませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.72,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:413760,414720}Ah…{NOTE:あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.60,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:414720,417600}There's nothing to apologize for.{NOTE:あっいやいや謝らなくていいんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:01.23,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:417600,421230}I didn't say it to make you depressed.{NOTE:僕は別に落ち込んでほしくて言ったわけじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.23,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:421230,425230}What Vice Captain Pappan wants to say is this:{NOTE:パパン副隊長が言いたいのはこういうことよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:11.03,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:425230,431030}The work of the squadron is to transform insight into evidence through steady research.{NOTE:書士隊のお仕事はひらめきを地道な研究で確証に変えていくこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:15.95,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:431030,435950}But insight is always the first step behind every great discovery.{NOTE:いつだって世紀の大発見も最初の一歩はひらめきですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.79,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:435950,437790}Ah, Vice Captain!{NOTE:あっ副隊長！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.37,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:437790,439370}I'll do my best!{NOTE:私頑張ります！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.12,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:439370,441120}Ah, sure!{NOTE:あっうん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.92,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:441120,442920}Good luck!{NOTE:頑張ってね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.46,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:442920,444460}Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:31.13,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:446380,451130}Pushing your own opinions onto children will only make them dislike you.{NOTE:自分の意見を押し付けるだけじゃ若い子に煙たがられるだけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.55,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:451130,453550}Uh, I guess I still have a world to learn.{NOTE:うっ…勉強になるっす…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.64,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:453550,456640}Wait, what are you doing here, Fifi?{NOTE:ってそういやティティ何でここにいるんすか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.72,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:456640,458720}You didn't know about it?{NOTE:あれ？聞いてませんでした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.10,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:458720,460100}About what?{NOTE:聞いてないよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:45.40,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:460100,465400}Captain Simone asked me to support you since she was uneasy leaving you alone.{NOTE:副隊長だけじゃ不安だからってシモーヌ隊長からサポートを頼まれたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.40,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:465400,466400}Eh!?{NOTE:えっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.53,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:466400,468530}Why are you looking away!?{NOTE:何で目をそらすの!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.44,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:468530,469440}{\i1}Huh…?{NOTE:あれ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.65,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:469440,471650}{\i1}I'm not trusted…?{NOTE:僕信頼されてない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.32,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:471650,474320}You're extremely capable.{NOTE:お前がいれば百人力だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.62,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:474320,475620}I'm counting on you.{NOTE:頼りにしてるぞ…}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.24,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:475620,476240}{\blur12\bord0\1c&H4F00FF&\shad0\alpha&H00&\t(\alpha&HFF&\fs60)}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.24,0:07:56.91,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:476240,476910}{\blur12\bord0\1c&H4F00FF&\shad0\alpha&H40&\t(\alpha&HFF&\fs60)}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.24,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:476910,477240}{\blur12\bord0\1c&H4F00FF&\shad0\alpha&H80&\t(\alpha&HFF&\fs60)}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.24,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:475620,476240}{\t(0,150,\1a&H55&\3a&H55&\4a&HE0&)}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:56.91,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:476240,476910}{\1a&H55&\3a&H55&\4a&HE0&\t(0,150,\1a&HAA&\3a&HAA&\4a&HE0&)}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.24,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:476910,477240}{\1a&HAA&\3a&HAA&\4a&HE0&\t(0,150,\alpha&HFF&)}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.71,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:477700,480710}Why did she smile like that?{NOTE:あの笑顔は何だったんすか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.83,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:480710,483830}Don't be so down. Think positive, positive!{NOTE:まあまあ元気出して。明るく明るく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.00,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:484960,487000}Kira-kira-nyaa!{NOTE:キラキラニャーン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:07.88,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:487000,487880}Oh…?{NOTE:あら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.63,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:489420,491630}{\i1}End of the survey day 1.{NOTE:調査１日目終了。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.47,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:491630,494470}{\i1}The number of traveling companions has increased unexpectedly.{NOTE:思わぬ形で同行者が増えた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:18.68,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:494470,498680}{\i1}There are different opinions about\Nthe circumstances for it. This will be a long journey.{NOTE:その理由に異論はあるものの旅は長い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:23.39,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:498680,503390}{\i1}However, one effective way to improve collaboration between fellow travelers is through communication.{NOTE:同行者との連携を深めるためにもコミュニケーションは有効だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.27,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:503390,504270}Lilia.{NOTE:リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.15,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:505900,508150}Would you like to eat mushrooms together?{NOTE:一緒に高層エリンギ食べない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.69,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:508150,509690}No, I'll pass.{NOTE:結構です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:34.41,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:509690,514410}A-Are you sure? The taste is so great I could eat it forever…{NOTE:そう言わずに…味は微妙だけど癖になるっていうか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.99,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:514410,515990}I have something I want to investigate.{NOTE:調べたいことがあるんで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.41,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:515990,517410}Excuse me.{NOTE:失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:41.25,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:517410,521250}{\i1}Communication with companions: failure.{NOTE:同行者とのｺﾐｭﾆｹｰｼｮﾝを図るも失敗。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:45.25,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:521250,525250}{\i1}Tonight I feel I can't connect with today's youth anymore.{NOTE:今どきの若者との間に断絶感を感じる夜であった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.26,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:528960,531260}I can't believe it.{NOTE:考えられないっすよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:57.34,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:531260,537340}When I was young, it was unthinkable to refuse my seniors' invitation.{NOTE:僕が若いころは先輩の誘いを断るなんてあり得ないことでしたよ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.14,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:537340,540140}Middle management has it hard, doesn't it?{NOTE:つらいわね中間管理職は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:04.39,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:540140,544390}As someone affiliated with the organization,\NI can understand your feelings.{NOTE:私も組織に属する立場だから副隊長の気持ち分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.81,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:544390,546810}Here you go. An Oiled Mushroom.{NOTE:はい。あぶり高層エリンギ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.86,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:546810,548860}Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:15.11,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:550900,555110}Only Fifi understands my feelings!{NOTE:僕の気持ちを分かってくれるのはティティだけっすよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.24,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:556410,558240}I understand you well.{NOTE:ちゃんと分かってるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:22.33,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:558240,562330}You seem lighthearted at first glance, but you're unexpectedly serious, Vice Captain Pappan.{NOTE:一見軽そうに見えて案外真面目なのよねパパン副隊長は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:26.29,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:562330,566290}Kids these days don't have a single bit of respect!{NOTE:最近後輩たちの風当たり強くって。こないだなんか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.34,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:567580,571340}Pappan is pretty small-minded, isn't he?{NOTE:パパン先輩って細かいですよね。みみっちいっていうか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.51,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:571340,573510}Don't you get tired of it?{NOTE:そういうの疲れません？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.43,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:573510,576430}What's so interesting about the vice captain's job?{NOTE:副隊長って何が楽しいんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.51,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:576430,578510}Well I'm sorry for being small-minded, alright!{NOTE:せこくて悪かったな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.85,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:578510,580850}Life's not always rainbows and unicorns!{NOTE:人生楽しいだけじゃないだろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:45.18,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:580850,585180}I am not as charismatic as Captain Simone.{NOTE:僕はｼﾓｰﾇ隊長のようにｶﾘｽﾏ性があるわけでもないし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.81,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:585180,588810}I don't have Lilia's intuition either.{NOTE:リリアみたいに直感がさえてるわけでもない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:53.11,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:588810,593110}That's why I need to do old fashioned boring work, step by step, step by step!{NOTE:だから地味にこつこつこつこつやるしかないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.15,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:593110,596150}Is it that bad? That's just how I work!{NOTE:悪いか！これが僕の仕事の流儀だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.70,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:600620,601700}Well said!{NOTE:よく言った！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.20,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:601700,603200}Thank you so much.{NOTE:ありがとうございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.79,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:603200,605790}Tonight let's drink to our heart's content!{NOTE:今夜はとことん飲みましょう！}
