Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.33,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:607670,609330}We need to get up early tomorrow, remember?{NOTE:あしたも早いんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.67,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:609330,610670}Ehh?{NOTE:え～}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.50,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:610670,613500}Please let me drink.{NOTE:飲ませてくださいよ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.47,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:616970,619470}Wake up, Vice Captain!{NOTE:副隊長起きて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.14,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:619470,621140}It's time to depart!{NOTE:もう出発の時間よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.47,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:621140,622470}Come on, now, get up!{NOTE:ほら起きて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.61,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:629980,632610}Are you okay, Vice Captain?{NOTE:副隊長大丈夫ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.36,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:632610,634360}O-Of course.{NOTE:も、もちろんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.24,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:635230,636240}Sorry I kept you waiting.{NOTE:お待たせ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.78,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:639780,640780}Eek!{NOTE:ああ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.49,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:642120,644490}S-Stand behind me!{NOTE:ぼ、僕の後ろに！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:46.16,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:644490,646160}Are you okay!?{NOTE:大丈夫ですか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.50,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:646160,649500}O-O-Of course! Leave it to me!{NOTE:だ、だ、大丈夫！ぼ、僕に任せて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:51.29,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:649500,651290}I wonder if we really can…{NOTE:任せていいのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.92,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:651290,653920}Everyone, don't move!{NOTE:み、みんな動かないで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:59.05,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:653920,659050}I-I will p-protect you!{NOTE:ぜ、絶対僕が君、君たちを守る、守るから！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:10:59.97,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:659050,659970}Huh!?{NOTE:ハッ！}
