Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.14,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:744590,746140}It's going to attack again…{NOTE:また襲ってくる気だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.89,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:746140,748890}W-What should we do?{NOTE:ど…どうしようこのままじゃ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.27,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:748890,750270}It'll be alright!{NOTE:大丈夫ですよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.18,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:750270,752180}Don't say it's your intuition again!{NOTE:また直感で言ってない!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.85,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:752180,753850}I said we'll be alright!{NOTE:大丈夫ですって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.10,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:753850,755100}Look!{NOTE:ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:38.32,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:755100,758320}Energy Drinks can't help us now!{NOTE:元気ドリンコなんて何の役にも立たないよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.65,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:758320,760650}We should find a place to hide instead!{NOTE:落とし穴とかの方がよっぽど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.94,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:760650,761940}Behind you!{NOTE:後ろ～!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:42.65,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:761940,762650}Oh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.70,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:763530,764700}Get down, Lilia!{NOTE:伏せろ！リリア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.91,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:770240,771910}Mr. Reverto!{NOTE:リヴェルトさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.58,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:771910,773580}Mr. Reverto! Mr. Reverto!{NOTE:リヴェルトさんリヴェルトさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:54.79,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:773580,774790}Look, it's an Energy Drink!{NOTE:元気ドリンコです！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.42,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:776580,778420}Thanks.{NOTE:こいつはありがたい。}
