Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.09,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:784720,786090}Do you have more?{NOTE:もう少しあるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.68,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:786090,788680}I was prepared for this.{NOTE:そんなこともあろうかと用意しておきました。}
