Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.14,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:789890,791140}B-But that's…!{NOTE:あっそれは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:11.97,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:791140,791970}Hmm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.23,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:798690,801230}That last one really hit the spot.{NOTE:こりゃ最後にすげえのきた…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.69,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:801230,802690}There's still a lot left!{NOTE:まだたくさんありますよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.99,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:808990,811990}{\i1}Preparation grants salvation.{NOTE:備えあれば憂いなしが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.50,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:811990,814500}{\i1}That's my traveling motto from now.{NOTE:…僕の旅のモットーであるが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:38.00,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:814500,818000}{\i1}It was this event that made me realize that no Energy Drink means no journey.{NOTE:ノー元気ドリンコノージャーニーを痛感した出来事だった。}
