Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.64,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:830890,832640}Get over here and eat.{NOTE:こっち来て食えよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:58.02,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:832640,838020}After my pathetic display out there,\NI don't feel like I have the right to eat.{NOTE:あんな醜態をさらしておいてご飯を頂く権利はないっす…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:01.19,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:838020,841190}So you're upset that you weren't able to stand upright despite fear?{NOTE:ビビって腰抜かしたこと落ち込んでんのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.40,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:841190,844400}Well, you were up against\Na monster, so it was only natural.{NOTE:モンスターが相手なんだから仕方ないだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:08.36,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:844400,848360}But someone in my position should protect their juniors.{NOTE:でも僕は後輩を守るべき立場なのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.37,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:848360,851370}I never expected you to protect me.{NOTE:あっそれは最初から期待してませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.24,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:851370,852240}Eh?{NOTE:えっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.87,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:852240,854870}I can take care of myself.{NOTE:自分の身は自分で守ります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.16,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:854870,856160}Using my wisdom.{NOTE:知恵を使って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.50,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:856160,858500}Here, have a donut.{NOTE:ドーナツでも食べなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.83,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:858500,859830}Thank you…{NOTE:ありがとうっす…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.55,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:861090,863550}You too. You were amazing.{NOTE:あなたにも。すてきだったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.26,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:863550,865260}Consider this a token of my gratitude.{NOTE:これ私の気持ち。}
