Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.99,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:887400,888990}Even though I'm a vice captain.{NOTE:副隊長なのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:52.07,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:888990,892070}I don't think it's related to you.{NOTE:それは関係ないと思うぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:57.87,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:892070,897870}My quest deals with Ebon Riders\Nand some channeling art.{NOTE:俺が頼まれたのはブラックライダーズとやらが使っている伝承技についてだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:01.33,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:897870,901330}I'm supposed to investigate what's the extent of their power.{NOTE:その実力はどれほどか調べてこいとさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.59,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:901330,906590}It's a special quest that normally I wouldn't take, but after I heard that Hakum was targeted…{NOTE:本来なら受けない特殊なクエストだがハクム村も被害を受けたと聞いたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.38,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:906590,909380}I couldn't stay silent any longer.{NOTE:…俺も黙っちゃいられねえよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:14.43,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:909380,914430}I went around several villages where they hunted for Kinship Stones to get some information.{NOTE:連中の情報を得るために絆石狩りに遭った村を幾つか回った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:20.14,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:914430,920140}That's how I heard that they seem to be collecting Kinship Stones to do a certain ritual.{NOTE:そこで聞いたがやつらはとある秘術を行うために絆石を集めているらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.06,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:920140,921060}Ah!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.23,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:921060,923230}That ritual…{NOTE:その秘術って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:27.90,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:923230,927900}It seems to allow a rider to synchronize with a monster and strengthens their power.{NOTE:何でもモンスターとシンクロして力を強化するものらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:30.82,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:927900,930820}So Lilia's intuition was right!?{NOTE:リリアの直感が正しかった！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.28,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:932490,934280}What do you mean?{NOTE:どういうことだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.33,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:934280,935330}Well, it's like this…{NOTE:実は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.46,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:938910,940460}I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:45.00,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:940460,945000}There might be someone in the Omi Valley\Nwho knows about this ritual.{NOTE:オミの谷にはその秘術について知る人間がいるかもしれないんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.51,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:946170,949510}But that place is a difficult area even for experienced Hunters.{NOTE:けどあそこは手だれのハンターでも苦戦する場所だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.22,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:949510,952220}Isn't it a little too high level for you?{NOTE:お前たちだけじゃちょっと心もとないんじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.97,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:954600,956970}I'll go with you.{NOTE:俺も一緒に行ってやるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:58.10,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:956970,958100}– Oh?\N– Terrific!{NOTE:—おっ？\\N—あら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.39,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:958100,959390}Really?{NOTE:マジっすか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:02.14,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:959390,962140}Tell your boss to get a proper reward ready.{NOTE:ボスに報酬を弾めと言っておけよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.94,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:962140,963940}I don't do freebies.{NOTE:これは別任務だからな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:04.81,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:963940,964810}Ah!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.23,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:964810,967230}Thanks! It'll be my pleasure!{NOTE:あざーっす！喜んで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.36,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:970070,973360}{\i1}Scrivener Journal Entry #20332.{NOTE:書士隊日誌ナンバー20332。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.03,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:973360,975030}{\i1}Reporter: Pappan.{NOTE:文責パパン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:22.12,Default,Simone,1,1,0,,{TIME:975030,982120}{\i1}During an ecological survey of monsters\Nin a certain village, I witnessed a fight between Riders.{NOTE:モンスターの生態調査で訪れたとある村にてライダー同士の決闘を目撃。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.04,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:982120,985040}{\i1}Why would a Rider fight a fellow Rider?{NOTE:ライダーがなぜライダーを襲う？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.67,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:985040,988670}{\i1}Riders bond with monsters using Kinship Stones.{NOTE:ライダーは絆石でモンスターと絆を結ぶ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:32.51,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:988670,992510}{\i1}What happens if one were to collect a lot of said Kinship Stones?{NOTE:その絆石をたくさん集めて何ができるというのだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:40.77,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:993880,1000770}{\i1}Can Kinship Stones, such as the ones belonging\Nto the Hakum Village's Riders, serve another purpose?{NOTE:ハクム村のライダーたちのように絆石に何か他の利用方法があるのだろうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:47.36,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000770,1007360}{\i1}If so, does the count matter\Nand is it the reason why they keep stealing them?{NOTE:だとしたらそれに数が必要だから奪ってまで集めているということか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:52.74,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007360,1012740}{\i1}What on earth are they going to do with the Kinship Stones they have gathered?{NOTE:集めた絆石でいったい何をしようとしているのだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:57.24,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012740,1017240}{\i1}At any rate, Kinship Stones seem to be at the center of it all.{NOTE:どうやら全ての理由は絆石にあるようだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.53,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017240,1018530}Hello.{NOTE:お疲れさまです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.20,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018530,1020200}Here are the documents you've requested.{NOTE:頼まれていた資料です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.91,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020200,1021910}Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.79,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021910,1024790}I wonder if Pappan is doing alright?{NOTE:今ごろパパンのやつ大丈夫ですかね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.54,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024790,1026540}What makes you worried about him?{NOTE:何を心配している？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:11.96,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026540,1031960}Well, recently he seems troubled\Nabout getting out of touch with his juniors.{NOTE:いや最近あいつ悩んでて後輩との接し方に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:15.38,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031960,1035380}Isn't that the reason why you asked Fifi to accompany him, Captain?{NOTE:だから隊長もティティに同行を頼んだんですよね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.51,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035380,1039510}What I was worried about wasn't Pappan's competence.{NOTE:私が心配していたのはパパンの力量ではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.72,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039510,1042720}Pappan might not look the part,\Nbut he's a serious, capable man.{NOTE:パパンはああ見えて真面目な男だからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:26.27,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042720,1046270}There are times when he overthinks things and runs around in circles, though.{NOTE:考え過ぎて空回りしてしまうことがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:31.40,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046270,1051400}I thought I could get him to enjoy\Nthe survey and relax more if I sent him with Fifi.{NOTE:ティティといればリラックスして気負わず調査に集中できると思ったのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.57,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051400,1052570}I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:36.15,Default,Scrivener,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052570,1056150}You sure do understand Pappan, don't you, Captain?{NOTE:隊長はパパンのことよく分かってますね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.57,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056150,1058570}Well, he is my right hand, after all.{NOTE:私の大事な右腕だからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.54,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062910,1064540}{\i1}Survey day 3.{NOTE:調査３日目。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.04,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064540,1067040}{\i1}We're pushing forward to Omi Valley.{NOTE:ひたすらオミの谷へ突き進む。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:56.34,Default,Pappan,1,1,0,,{TIME:1067040,1076340}{\i1}Also known as the Hunter's training ground, it was once inhabited with variety of monsters and just as many Hunters.{NOTE:ハンターの修練場と呼ばれたオミの谷はかつては多種多様なモンスターが成育し多くのハンターたちでにぎわう場所だったと聞いている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:18:00.26,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076340,1080260}{\i1}However, this has changed completely\Nover time and, now, there's nothing to be seen.{NOTE:しかしそこは見る影もないほど様変わりしていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.39,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082010,1084390}Looks like there's no one around here.{NOTE:誰もいないみたいっすね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:09.06,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084390,1089060}In the past, it was a valley filled with many monsters\Nand vibrant villages full of Hunters…{NOTE:昔はモンスターも多くハンターや村人でにぎわう谷だったんだがな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.73,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090310,1091730}Excuse me!{NOTE:すみませーん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.48,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091730,1093480}Is anyone there?{NOTE:誰かいませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.57,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094570,1096570}Doesn't look like it.{NOTE:誰もいないみたいだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096570,1097820}Yeah…{NOTE:はい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.74,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097820,1099740}We can't do anything about it.{NOTE:しょうがないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.45,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099740,1101450}Sometimes things just turn out like this.{NOTE:こういうときもある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.74,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101450,1103740}But let's not admit defeat just yet.\NWe'll continue the investigation.{NOTE:諦めずに調査を続けよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.91,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103740,1104910}All right.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.66,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104910,1105660}Oh?{NOTE:おっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.08,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105660,1107080}There seems to be someone inside.{NOTE:誰かいるみたいだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.29,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108170,1109290}Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.92,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111130,1112920}Excuse me, I'm coming in.{NOTE:すみません！失礼します！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.81,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125430,1126810}Who is it?{NOTE:誰じゃな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.06,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128060,1129060}Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫ですか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:55.32,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132730,1135320}Thank you. It got easier.{NOTE:ありがとう。楽になった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:19:01.41,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136110,1141410}What on earth brings you to this village?{NOTE:それであんた方いったいこんな村に何の用じゃ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141410,1143950}I'm Lilia of the Royal Scriveners.{NOTE:王立書士隊のリリアといいます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:07.83,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143950,1147830}I came here looking for clues about this picture.{NOTE:私たちこの絵について知りたくてやって来ました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.04,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147830,1150040}Is that…{NOTE:それは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.50,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150040,1153500}Well, if it isn't the picture my grandfather painted!{NOTE:あっそれはわしの祖父が描いた絵じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.34,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1153500,1154340}Eh!?{NOTE:えっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:21.13,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156050,1161130}When I was young, my grandfather told me stories about the village in this picture.{NOTE:幼いころ祖父からこの絵に描かれた村の話を聞いた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.76,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161130,1164760}That village seems to have passed down a certain ritual for generations.{NOTE:その村は深い山に閉ざされた秘境で…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.89,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164760,1168890}It was performed in secret,\Ndeep in the unexplored area of the mountains.{NOTE:…代々伝わる秘密の術を行っていたらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:31.77,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168890,1171770}What kind of ritual?{NOTE:その術とはどんな術なんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:36.02,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171770,1176020}A secret art passed down to a village named Kuang, which no longer exists today.{NOTE:今はなきクアン村に伝わる秘術らしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.90,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176020,1176900}Secret art!?{NOTE:秘術！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.40,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176900,1179400}A rite held in secret?{NOTE:内緒の儀式ってことっすか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.11,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179400,1182110}So Kuang Village means that…{NOTE:クアン村といったら確か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.12,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182110,1185120}I heard that it was destroyed several years ago.{NOTE:数年前に滅びたと聞いている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.45,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185120,1188450}It was subjected to the Black Blight.{NOTE:黒の凶気に襲われてな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:52.58,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188450,1192580}But I've been hearing some gossip about it lately.{NOTE:じゃが最近になってある噂話を耳にした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.63,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192580,1195630}Seems that someone from Kuang Village\Nsurvived the destruction.{NOTE:クアン村の生き残りがいると。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:59.92,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195630,1199920}That person is said to have a mysterious kinship with an ice-type Barioth.{NOTE:氷牙竜ベリオロスと不思議な絆を結ぶ者らしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.09,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199920,1201090}Miss Avinia!{NOTE:アユリアさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.76,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201090,1203760}Avinia survived Kuang!?{NOTE:アユリアさんがクアン村の生き残り!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.72,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203760,1205720}That means…{NOTE:それって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.77,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205720,1208770}The Ebon Riders abducted Miss Avinia…{NOTE:ブラックライダーズがアユリアさんを誘拐したのは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.64,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208770,1211640}…to obtain Kuang Village's secrets?{NOTE:…クアン村の秘術を手に入れるため？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:16.06,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211640,1216060}What if that secret art falls into bad hands?{NOTE:その秘術が悪いやつらの手に渡ったらどうなる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.40,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216060,1218400}A calamity will happen…{NOTE:悲劇が待っているじゃろう…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:26.03,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222490,1226030}Kuang Village is over that mountain.{NOTE:クアン村はあの山の向こうじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:29.79,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226030,1229790}The path is severed, so it's not going to be easy.{NOTE:道は断たれていて行くすべはないが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229790,1230950}We'll be okay.{NOTE:大丈夫です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.71,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230950,1231710}Eh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.92,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231710,1233920}Why? Your intuition again?{NOTE:どうして？また直感？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:39.46,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233920,1239460}No. I know that I can't make it,\Nbut I'm positive Lute and Cheval can.{NOTE:いえ私は無理でもリュートとシュヴァルならきっと見つけると思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:44.05,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239460,1244050}I will return to Gildegaran\Nand tell them about Kuang Village.{NOTE:私ギルデカランに戻って２人にクアン村のことを伝えようと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.60,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245390,1247600}Thank you very much.{NOTE:ありがとうございました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.72,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247600,1249720}It was very helpful.{NOTE:とっても助かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.35,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249720,1252350}Be careful on your journey back.{NOTE:道中気を付けてな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.64,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252350,1253640}We will.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:21:00.73,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253640,1260730}Oh, and one more thing. A few years ago\Na group like you visited this village.{NOTE:そうじゃ…そういえば数年前にお前さんたちのようにこの村を訪ねてきた者がおった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.61,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260730,1262610}What did they ask you about?{NOTE:何を聞きにですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:06.11,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262610,1266110}They also asked about Kuang Village survivors.{NOTE:クアン村の生き残りについて聞いてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.99,Default,Townfolk,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266110,1269990}They were desperately looking for them.{NOTE:それはもう必死で捜しておった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:21.13,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276420,1281130}The group who visited him back then must have been Avinia's acquaintances.{NOTE:数年前に訪ねてきた人ってアユリアさんの知り合いですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.42,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281130,1284420}They might be Kuang survivors too.{NOTE:その人もクアン村の生き残りかもしれない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.84,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284420,1286840}…it's just my intuition though.{NOTE:…ってただの直感だけど！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.51,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286840,1290510}"Every great discovery starts from an insight", was it?{NOTE:「世紀の大発見も最初はひらめきから｣ですよね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.69,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293100,1296690}I think that our Vice Captain's intuition is quite sharp.{NOTE:副隊長の直感もなかなかさえてると思うわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:37.85,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296690,1297850}That's right!{NOTE:そうですよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.48,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297850,1300480}I'm proud to have you as my senior!{NOTE:副隊長は私の自慢の先輩です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.73,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300480,1301730}You really mean that!?{NOTE:本当に!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.95,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301730,1304950}But the one I respect most is Captain Simone.{NOTE:でも一番尊敬してるのはシモーヌ隊長です！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:50.58,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306910,1310580}Lilia didn't mean that in a bad way.{NOTE:リリアは全然悪気がないからぐさっと刺さるわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:53.12,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310580,1313120}Well, she's proud to have me. That's plenty.{NOTE:自慢って言われただけでじゅうぶんっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.67,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314410,1316670}Alright, we're going back to Gildegaran.{NOTE:よしギルデカランへ帰るぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.46,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1316670,1318460}Yeah!{NOTE:おーっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.00,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318460,1320000}{\i1}Survey report.{NOTE:調査報告。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:05.13,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320000,1325130}{\i1}I didn't manage to solve the mystery\Nbehind the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:今回の旅でﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞの謎を解き明かすことはできなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:10.18,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325130,1330180}{\i1}However, I obtained a few important clues.{NOTE:しかし幾つかの手掛かりを導き出すことができた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:16.60,Default,Pappan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330180,1336600}{\i1}And I know that, some day, these clues will aid in solving the mystery of the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:これらはいつか必ずブラックライダーズの全容を解き明かすためのきっかけとなるはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:28.95,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341690,1348950}I am searching for the Kinship Stones\Nof priests from your hometown, Kuang Village.{NOTE:私はお前の故郷クアン村の神官が持つ絆石を捜している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.74,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348950,1350740}Kinship Stones?{NOTE:絆石？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:37.08,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350740,1357080}You're a survivor from Kuang Village.\NYou should know of those Kinship Stones.{NOTE:クアン村の生き残りであるお前ならその絆石を知っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:40.92,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357080,1360920}Or maybe you possess one yourself?{NOTE:あるいは持っているのでは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.59,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360920,1364590}I have no idea about what you're talking about.{NOTE:そのような絆石のことは知りませんでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:50.30,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364590,1370300}Besides, you took away my Kinship Stone.{NOTE:それに私の絆石は奪われましたあなたたちに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:53.01,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370300,1373010}I don't remember my childhood.{NOTE:幼いころのことは覚えていないんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:54.43,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373010,1374430}Nothing…{NOTE:何も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:56.43,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1374430,1376430}Not even my family.{NOTE:家族のことさえ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:59.48,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376430,1379480}I want to remember it all myself!{NOTE:思い出せるものなら思い出したいです！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.73,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1379480,1381730}I know…{NOTE:私は知っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:06.74,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1381730,1386740}I know about Kuang Village's priests\Nas well as the secrets that they control.{NOTE:クアン村の神官もその者たちが操る秘術も。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:17.91,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1395200,1397910}I know {\i1}you{\i0}.{NOTE:私はお前を知っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:24.00,Default,Anvis,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399620,1404000}Sooner or later, everything will fall into my hands.{NOTE:いずれその全てをわがものとしてみせる！}
